&lt;li&gt;Partnering closely with Art and Design teams to craft fun, engaging player experiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing priorities effectively while staying organized and agile in a fast-paced environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clearly articulating, presenting, and defending design decisions to cross-functional stakeholders&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We’re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
